{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967380/extras/description_title_copy.png?t=1737984866\" /><strong><i>DEAD DETENTION</i></strong> is a scribbly <i>coming of age/adventure/comedy\u00a0</i>visual novel that takes place entirely within a <i>bored high schooler's exercisebook</i>. In it, you play as <i>Max</i>, a nerdy teen turned dooms day survivor, as he and his new friends try to <strong>get to safety!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967380/extras/description_headings_copy_STORY.png?t=1737984866\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">14 year old <strong>Max</strong> is given a detention for falling asleep in class - but a zombie outbreak suddenly interrupts it! Senior student <strong>Naomi </strong>saves him from a deadly attack, but can't leave campus without <strong>her lost sister Sora</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Deciding to stay behind and help her, Max and Naomi begin their quest to find Sora, while struggling to <strong>survive the quickly spreading virus...</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967380/extras/description_headings_copy_choices.png?t=1737984866\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shape Max by making choices that are <strong>brave, scared, nice or mean</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All your choices will compound and lead to <strong>1 of 3 endings</strong>, including a special <strong>true ending</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967380/extras/description_headings_copy_MICROGAMES.png?t=1737984866\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete <strong>quick microgames</strong> throughout the story to swing your bat, run from zombies, climb ladders, and much more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each episode builds to a fun <strong>boss challenge</strong> - such as target shooting and boxing!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features 3 difficulties, including an <strong>unlockable Hard Mode</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>DEAD DETENTION</strong></i> is a rescribbled and fully remade version of the cult flash series. It features <strong>5 episodes of chaotic fun</strong>, plus <strong>a special epilogue</strong> unlocked by achieving either of the good endings.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Episode 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/356c48229735e5bfea73ff5dc2ee4bc4ff0dbf7b.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/356c48229735e5bfea73ff5dc2ee4bc4ff0dbf7b.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/356c48229735e5bfea73ff5dc2ee4bc4ff0dbf7b.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/356c48229735e5bfea73ff5dc2ee4bc4ff0dbf7b.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/f528ed547626766b8c0418fda2fdd8517683cb63.jpg"},{"name":"True Ending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/b51bc8af55a8714043e38932c21c1e1b1ac6ec5c.jpg"},{"name":"Sad Ending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/b51bc8af55a8714043e38932c21c1e1b1ac6ec5c.jpg"},{"name":"After Story","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2967380/356c48229735e5bfea73ff5dc2ee4bc4ff0dbf7b.jpg"},